    </table>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "example-1-cos32--43--78"
    }}>{`Example 1: cos(32) = 4.3 / 7.8`}</h2>
    <p>{`When used in our code, we can make it look like the following:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-ts"
      }}>{`import * as Mathium from "mathiumjs";

function cosineCalc(adj, hypotenuse) {
  let formula = Mathium.findCosine(adj, hypotenuse);
  return formula;
}

// Test the function
console.log(cosineCalc(4.3, 7.8));
`}</code></pre>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "example-2-cos22--2784--124"
    }}>{`Example 2: cos(22) = 27.84 / 12.4`}</h2>
    <p>{`When used in our code, we can make it look like the following:`}</p>
